                <note rend="inline" type="source">580.7A3/420: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Chargé in Great Britain</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Atherton</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1929-05-29T20:00:00-04:00"
                            >May 29, 1929—8 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>131. For White. Your 131, May 28, noon. Department considers that in order to
                    avoid possible misunderstanding and the necessity for making explanations you
                    should follow instructions March 28 concerning reservation.</p>
                <p>This Government has not signed the Counterfeiting Convention.<note n="9a"
                        xml:id="d222fn9a">See <ref target="#pg_394">pp. 394</ref> ff.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Stimson</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
